body:
I'm seeing this as well as of last night. 

Its preceded by many warnings about `VariableVersion`:

```
    /private/var/folders/s1/_v14lsc56tv44hm304m07vn40000gq/T/pip-az42dap4-build/torch/csrc/autograd/variable_version.h:77:10: warning: class 'VariableVersion' was previously declared as a struct [-Wmismatched-tags]
      friend class VariableVersion;
```

But the first error is the one about `call to 'recordTrace' is ambiguous`. 

I went back, and I get a good install as late as commit 5989b05ecce4c41d69b4d41280a5ee47d2bb9fa4
